channel.title: Dream of Reality - BobTheGUYYYYY [Ambient, chill, soundscape]
channel.description:
Imagine something, if you will.
As you listen to this song, imagine you have been trapped in endless limbo for eons. Imagine that a gateway through the cosmos opens up before you and you finally get your first glimpse of Earth in centuries.
I hope you enjoy it. Click the cover art to start listening.
[![reality|500x500](upload://pXf9TMpatLACGgz2qMGw5zey7ni.png)](https://soundcloud.com/bobtheguyyyyy/dream-of-reality-bobtheguyyyyy)
